rows.label: qst202304_msg001
rows.name:
It's a pretty humongous library, right?
There's more than ten million books
here, y'know.

rows.label: qst202304_msg002
rows.name:
Well, I don't know much about this
kind of thing, but it sounds like a lot!

rows.label: qst202304_msg003
rows.name:
This place has basically got every
single book, from every time and place.
If there's a clue, it must be here.

rows.label: qst202304_msg004
rows.name:
Yeah! No doubt! You hear that,
mega-beast? We're comin' for ya!

rows.label: qst202304_msg005
rows.name:
Hey, why don't we split up and look
for it?

rows.label: qst202304_msg007
rows.name: All that searching turned up nothing...

rows.label: qst202304_msg009
rows.name:
No, it's hardly your fault, Saika.
It's fine.

rows.label: qst202304_msg011
rows.name:
I guess getting your hopes up that high
only sets you up for disappointment...

rows.label: qst202304_msg012
rows.name:
Ah, Yaegiri. It breaks my heart to see
you so crestfallen.

rows.label: qst202304_msg013
rows.name:
Someone must know about this
sealed-up legendary beast! Wouldn't
be much of a legend if they didn't...
